testcase.title: Export Search Service for BrokerResearch dataset verifying all the column names

steps.title: I am authenticated user accessing "SOAP" API

I pass a "applicationId = ngapi#1756 and userId = API and dataSet = brokerresearch and searchQuery = cancer and queryLanguage = ssql and returnFields = brokerResearchId,brokerResearchHeadline,brokerResearchContributor,brokerResearchAuthors,brokerResearchCompanies,brokerResearchDrugsRelated,brokerResearchIndicationsRelated,brokerResearchTargetsRelated,brokerResearchSubjects,brokerResearchRegions,brokerResearchCountries,brokerResearchIndustries,brokerResearchLanguage,brokerResearchReportType,brokerResearchReleaseDate and returnLimit = 10 and offset = 0 and expectedValues = expsearch_BR_061.xls and exportFormat = MS-EXCEL and wrapText = True" as parameter to "asyncExportAdvancedSearchResults" operation
I call poll async "180" times with interval "1" seconds with input "applicationId = ngapi#1756 and userId = API" I should get the response
check the requested file is found in the following path "expsearch_BR_061.xls"

check for all the columns "brokerResearchId,Headline,Contributor,Authors,Companies,Drugs,Indications,Targets,Subjects,Regions,Countries/Territories,Industries,Language,Report Type,Release Date" in the file
